Masala - Easy Potato stuffing for dosa.. 500g potatoes washed well 200g finely chopped onion 1 teaspoon finely chopped ginger 1 teaspoon finely chopped green chilies (increase as per spice level needed) 10-15 curry leaves 2-3 teaspoons Oil 1 teaspoon mustard seeds 1 teaspoon chana dal 1/2 teaspoon haldi salt to taste chopped coriander Boil, peel & roughly mash the potatoes. In a pan/ kadhai heat the oil crackle mustard seeds & add chana dal. Roast for 30 seconds Add in ginger, green chilies, onion, curry leaves and saute until transparent. Add haldi, salt, cook for 1-2 minutes Add mashed potatoes, mix well & cook for a few minutes Add chopped coriander leaves #masala #dosa #potato #stuffing #southindianfood #bangalorefoodblogger
